OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers, heavy at times, continuing
OL,7,Fthis evening and overnight, still with
OL,8,Fthe risk of hail mixed in. Rather
OL,9,Fchilly, but the brisk northerly wind
OL,10,Fand cloud preventing a frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FWinds not as strong as
OL,13,FWednesday, but scattered, blustery
OL,14,Fshowers continue with some with hail
OL,15,Fand thunder possible. Feeling cool
OL,16,Fwith temperatures remaining below
OL,17,Faverage for mid-May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
